songs.comment_text: For a quick brief story behind this boss battle, the badger people of the West were fighting against the titans like any of the places. They used green crystals mounted on turrets and guns (which you can see in-game and by talking with the old badger). These green crystals have regenerative properties (which they used to imprison the Titans) and many of the badgers have been imprisoned, but the general, instead the general was corrupted by the crystal driving him mad as insane as he immediately attempts to kill you and attacks in ruthless and hard to predict motions. In the game, he is known as the 'hanged man' which is one of the tarot cards that mean wisdom and sacrifice, this just further proves that he has sacrificed something most likely his life to defeat the Titans. Now, whenever I see this boss I can never look at him the same especially when you put him out of his misery.
